"""Test parsing of ignition delay data points for shock tube file.
        """
file_path = os.path.join('testfile_st2.xml')
filename = pkg_resources.resource_filename(__name__, file_path)
tree = etree.parse(filename)
root = tree.getroot()
properties = {}
properties = parse_files_XML.get_datapoints(properties, root)
np.testing.assert_allclose(properties['temperature'], 1264.2 * units.kelvin)
np.testing.assert_allclose(properties['ignition-delay'], 291.57 * units.us)
